text: Christina Gokey-Smith (born November 28, 1973) is an American professional racing cyclist. She rides for the Pepper Palace p/b The Happy Tooth team. Before becoming a cyclist she competed in equestrianism. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:American female cyclists Category:People from Fort Worth, Texas Category:Sportspeople from Texas
